  h2.header__bottom-border-left Banking &amp; Settlement
  p.lead Exactly what you charge, deposited directly into your bank account.

  h3 Bank Deposits
  p Settlement payments happen automatically, every business day. BitPay collects and deposits all payments processed from the previous business day directly to your bank or bitcoin wallet, according to your settlement preferences.
  p We protect merchants on our platform by maintaining enterprise-level legal and compliance standards. Tiered processing limits apply based on verification level; these limits can be raised through <a href=https://bitpay.com/merchant-compliance> compliance verification </a>.

  h3 Currencies
  p Depending on your location, minimum settlement amounts and deposit timings will vary.

  h3 Settlement Timing
  p Depending on your location, minimum settlement amounts and deposit timings will vary.

  h4 US Dollars (USD)
  p Settlement in USD is available via ACH to banks in the USA, and will appear in your bank account after two business days. The minimum settlement is 20 USD.

  h4 Canadian Dollars (CAD)
  p The minimum settlement is 100 CAD. Settlement will appear in your bank account after two business days.

  h4 Australian Dollars (AUD)
  p The minimum settlement is 1,000 AUD. Settlement will appear in your bank account after two business days.

  h4 Pounds Sterling (GBP)
  p The minimum settlement is 1,000 GBP. Settlement will appear in your bank account after two business days.

  h4 Mexican Pesos (MXN)
  p The minimum settlement is 10,000 MXN. Settlement will appear in your bank account after two business days.

  h4 New Zealand Dollar (NZD)
  p The minimum settlement is 1,000 NZD. Settlement will appear in your bank account after two business days.

  h4 Bitcoin (BTC)
  p If you choose to take settlement in bitcoin, BitPay will forward bitcoin payments to your bitcoin address on file. The minimum settlement is 0.01 BTC.

  h4 Euros (EUR)
  p Settlement will appear in your bank account after one business day. The minimum settlement is 20 EUR.

